{
    "1152:0": "saptamaparivartaḥ |",
    "1152:1": "sāsravabhāvanāmārgānantaramanāsravo bhāvanāmārgo vaktavyaḥ |",
    "1152:2": "sa ca dvividha iti |",
    "1152:3": "prathamamabhinirhāralakṣaṇaṃ bhāvanāmārgaṃ vaktuṃ svabhāvābhidhānādāha |",
    "1152:4": "atha khalvāyuṣmānityādi |",
    "1152:5": "tathāgatajñānasya niṣpādanahetutvātsarvajñajñānapariniṣpattiḥ |",
    "1152:6": "sarvajñatvamiti rūpādyaviparītadarśanaṃ svabhāva ityarthaḥ |",
    "1152:7": "evamityādivacanena labdhaprasādātiśayatvādabhinirhārasya vistareṇa jñānasvābhāvyaparidīpanārthamāha |",
    "1152:8": "avabhāsakarītyādi |",
    "1152:9": "uṣmagatajñānālokatvādavabhāsakarī |",
    "1152:10": "kāyavāṅmanobhiḥ praṇāmānnamaskaromi |",
    "1152:11": "yasmānnamaskārārhatvānnamaskaraṇīyā |",
    "1152:12": "mūrdhāvasthāprāptatvenāśraddhādibhirasaṃsargādanupaliptā |",
    "1152:13": "kṣāntisvabhāvatvenāpāyasaṃvartanīyakarmavigamāt sarvalokanirupalepā |",
    "1152:14": "agradharmarūpatvena lokottarajñānodayahetutvādālokakarī |",
    "1152:15": "duḥkhadharmajñānakṣāntyā svadarśanaprahātavyatraidhātukakleśaprahāṇāt sarvatraidhātukavitimirakarī |",
    "1152:16": "dharmajñānena vimuktisākṣātkaraṇāt sarvakleśadṛṣṭyandhakārāpanetrī |",
    "1152:17": "anvayajñānakṣāntyā&#39;",
    "1152:18": "&#39;",
    "1152:19": "ryadharmānvayāvagamādāśrayaṇīyā |",
    "1152:20": "anvayajñānena niścayāvadhāraṇādagrakarī |",
    "1152:21": "samudaye dharmajñānakṣāntyādibhiścaturbhiḥ kṣaṇaiḥ pūrvavadvyāpārakaraṇādyathākramaṃ bodhipakṣāṇāṃ dharmāṇāṃ kṣemakarī,",
    "1152:22": "ālokakarī,",
    "1152:23": "sarvabhayopadravaprahīṇā&#39;",
    "1152:24": "&#39;",
    "1152:25": "lokakarīti padacatuṣṭayaṃ yojyam |",
    "1152:26": "māṃsadivyaprajñābuddhadharmacakṣuḥparigrahaṃ kṛtvā pūrvavannirodhe dharmajñānakṣāntyā mārgadarśayitrī |",
    "1152:27": "dharmajñānena cakṣuranvayajñānakṣāntyā mṛdumadhyādhimātravipakṣāpagamenāryadharmānvayāvagamānmohatamastimiravikaraṇī |",
    "1152:28": "anvayajñānena niścayāvadhāraṇādvitimirakaraṇī |",
    "1152:29": "mārge tathaiva dharmajñānakṣāntyā&#39;karaṇī |",
    "1152:30": "dharmajñānena mārgāvatāraṇī |",
    "1152:31": "anvayajñānakṣāntyā sarvajñatā |",
    "1152:32": "anvayajñānena sarvakleśajñeyāvaraṇāvāsanānusandhiprahīṇatāmupādāyānutpādikā |",
    "1152:33": "sāsravabhāvanāmārgeṇa kuśaladharmaprasavanādanirodhitā |",
    "1152:34": "māyopamatvādanāsravābhinirhārabhāvanāmārgarūpeṇa sadāvasthānādanutpannāniruddhā |",
    "1152:35": "atyantaviśuddhibhāvanāmārgasvabhāvenātiśayahitakāriṇītvāt svalakṣaṇaśūnyatāmupādāya mātā |",
    "1152:36": "sa ca mṛdumadhyādhimātrabhedāttrividha iti yathākramaṃ daśabalakarī,",
    "1152:37": "anavamardanī,",
    "1152:38": "nāthakarīti padatrayamuktam |",
    "1152:39": "ānantaryamārgatayā sarvasaṃsāraprahāṇāt saṃsārapratipakṣaḥ |",
    "1152:40": "kūṭaḥ sāmagrī tatra tiṣṭhatīti hetupratyayajanyo bhāvastathoktastatpratiṣedhādakūṭasthatāmupādāya vimuktimārgeṇa sarvaguṇasampadabhimukhībhāvāt sarvadharmasvabhāvavidarśanī,",
    "1152:41": "paścādevaṃ samadhigatatatvānāṃ yathāśayaṃ triyānadharmadeśanayā paripūrṇatriparivartadvādaśākāradharmacakrapravartanītyevameṣāṃ padānāmarthanirdeśo vācya iti pūrvācāryāḥ |",
    "1152:42": "tatra trayaḥ parivartā dvādaśākārā yasmin dharmacakra iti vigrahaḥ |",
    "1152:43": "tatrāmī trayaḥ parivartāḥ |",
    "1152:44": "yaduta idaṃ duḥkhamāryasatyaṃ tat khalvabhijñāya parijñeyaṃ parijñātam |",
    "1152:45": "idaṃ duḥkhasamudaya āryasatyaṃ tadabhijñāya prahātavyaṃ prahīṇam |",
    "1152:46": "idaṃ duḥkhanirodhaṃ āryasatyaṃ tadabhijñāya sākṣātkartavyaṃ sākṣātkṛtam |",
    "1152:47": "idaṃ duḥkhanirodhagāminī pratipadāryasatyam |",
    "1152:48": "tat khalvabhijñāya bhāvayitavyaṃ bhāvitaṃ mayeti bhikṣavaḥ pūrvamanuśruteṣu dharmeṣu yoniśomanasikurvataḥ pratyakṣārthatvādanāsravā prajñā cakṣurudayādi |",
    "1152:49": "niḥsaṃśayatvājjñānaṃ bhūtārthatvādvidyā viśuddhatvādvuddhirudayādītyetatkriyāpadamekaikasmin satye triṣvapi yojyam |",
    "1152:50": "ataḥ pratyekañcaturṇāmāryasatyānāṃ triparivartanātriparivartam |",
    "1152:51": "cakṣurityādayaścākārāścatvārastriparivartanāt pratisatyaṃ traya ityato dvādaśākāram |",
    "1152:52": "etāvataiva jagadarthasampādanāt paripūrṇaṃ triparivartadvādaśākāraṃ dharmacakramiva dharmacakraṃ yat prathamato vārāṇasyāṃ bhāṣitaṃ sūtram |",
    "1152:53": "yathā rājñaścakravartinaścakraratnamagresaraṃ sarvastu balakāyastadevānusaran paścādgacchati,",
    "1152:54": "tathā sakalatrailokyādhipatestathāgatasya tat sūtramagrataḥ kṛtvā sarvo deśanādharmaḥ prabhavati |",
    "1152:55": "atastanmāturādhipatyena pravartata iti |",
    "1152:56": "bhagavatī tathoktā |",
    "1152:57": "śreṣṭhatāṃ pratipādayitumāha |",
    "1152:58": "kathaṃ bhagavānityādi |",
    "1152:59": "pariharannāha |",
    "1152:60": "yathā śāriputretyādi |",
    "1152:61": "śāstarīva pratipattyādividhānānnānyathāvabuddhatvasamprāptiriti śreṣṭhatā kathitā |",
    "1152:62": "kuta iti kasmāddhetorityarthaḥ |",
    "1152:63": "tadevāha |",
    "1152:64": "kinnidāneti |",
    "1152:65": "etannidāneti puṇyaskandhābhibhavahetukā |",
    "1152:66": "abhinirhāraśreṣṭhatādhikāre pariṇāmanāmanaskārapuṇyaskandhahetukā pṛcchā kimarthamiti ceducyate |",
    "1152:67": "yatra hi nāma sāsravapariṇāmanāmanaskārasyedṛśī śreṣṭhatā yadbalādaprameyadānādipuṇyaskandhābhibhavo jātastatra sutarāmevānāsravabhāvanāmārgasyeti kathanāya pariṇāmābhibhūtapuṇyaskandhahetukā pṛcchā kṛtā |",
    "1152:68": "atiśayārthamevāha |",
    "1152:69": "apitu khalu punarityādi |",
    "1152:70": "sarvajñatāmārgāvatārāyeti |",
    "1152:71": "buddhatvaprāpakamārgapramuditādibhūmiṣvavatāranimittam |",
    "1152:72": "apariṇāyakamabhavyamiti |",
    "1152:73": "sārathibhāvarahitamayogyam |",
    "1152:74": "dānamityādi |",
    "1152:75": "tatra dānaṃ dharmābhiṣābhayabhedātrividham |",
    "1152:76": "tathā śīlamakuśalanivṛttikuśalapravṛttisattvārthakriyārūpeṇa trividham |",
    "1152:77": "tathā kṣāntirapi dharmanidhyānaduḥkhādhivāsanaparāpakāramarṣaṇātmikā trividhā |",
    "1152:78": "tathā vīryamapi sannāhakuśalasattvārthaprayogabhedātrividham |",
    "1152:79": "tathā dhyānaṃ guṇasattvārthakleśapratipakṣasukhābhinirhārātpūrvavattrividhamiti |",
    "1152:80": "jātyandhabhūtamiti |",
    "1152:81": "utpadyamānameva saṃvṛtiparamārthasatyasakalasattvārthālambanabhedātrividhaprajñācakṣuṣā vihīnam |",
    "1152:82": "kutaḥ punariti |",
    "1152:83": "kasmātpunarnaivetyarthaḥ |",
    "1152:84": "pāramitānāmadheyameva kathayati |",
    "1152:85": "pāramitāśabdamiti |",
    "1152:86": "āsāñcakṣuḥpratilambha iti |",
    "1152:87": "dānādipāramitānāṃ dharmatācakṣuḥsamanvāgamaḥ |",
    "1152:88": "sarvadharmānabhisaṃskṛtiṃ pratipādayitumāha |",
    "1152:89": "kathaṃ bhagavan bodhisattvenetyādi |",
    "1152:90": "pariharannāha |",
    "1152:91": "rūpasyetyādi |",
    "1152:92": "māyopamatayā rūpāderadhigamo māturabhinirhāra ityarthaḥ |",
    "1152:93": "upasaṃharannāha |",
    "1152:94": "evamanabhisaṃskāreṇetyādi |",
    "1152:95": "tathatārūpatvāt sarvadharmaviśeṣānutpādanenādhigamo prayogo&#39;",
    "1152:96": "nabhisaṃskārastena skandhānāmadhigama iti yāvat |",
    "1152:97": "kvacidanabhinirhāreṇeti pāṭhastatrāpyayamevārtho grāhyaḥ |",
    "1152:98": "sarvadharmānupalambhenābhisamayārpaṇārthamāha |",
    "1152:99": "evamabhinirhṛtetyādi |",
    "1152:100": "na kaściddharmamarpayatīti |",
    "1152:101": "yathopalambhādiviparyāsastathā na kaścidadhigamadharmaṃ yogisantāne samutpādayati tadā prajñāpāramiteti saṃkhyāṃ gacchatyaviparyastatvāditi matiḥ |",
    "1152:102": "sarvajñatāyāstvarpaṇaṃ yuktamanyathā nirarthikaiva prajñāpāramitetyabhiprāyavānāha |",
    "1152:103": "kimiyambhagavannityādi |",
    "1152:104": "viparyāsadvāreṇa nārpayatītyāha |",
    "1152:105": "na yathopalambha ityādi |",
    "1152:106": "tatropalambho bāhyārthopalambhaḥ |",
    "1152:107": "nāma catvāro&#39;",
    "1152:108": "rūpiṇaḥ skandhāḥ |",
    "1152:109": "abhisaṃskāro māyopamamevedaṃ tattvamityādicittābhogaḥ prakārāntaravyavacchedenānyathārpaṇamityāha |",
    "1152:110": "kathaṃ tarhītyādi |",
    "1152:111": "yathā kauśika nārpayati tathārpayatīti |",
    "1152:112": "yena prakāreṇa māyopamatayā kaścidabhiniveśaṃ viparyāsaṃ nārpayati tathā sarvajñatāmarpayatītyarthaḥ |",
    "1152:113": "na kiñciddharmamutpādayatīti vaiyavadānikaṃ na kiñciddharmaṃ nirodhayatīti sāṃkleśikam |",
    "1152:114": "pratyupasthitetyanutpādāya |",
    "1152:115": "anupasthitetyanirodhāyeti yojyam |",
    "1152:116": "evamapyabhiniveśo bandhanamityāha |",
    "1152:117": "sacedevamityādi |",
    "1152:118": "prayogadarśanabhāvanāviśeṣamārgeṣu yathākramaṃ dūrīkariṣyati riktīkariṣyati tucchīkariṣyati na kariṣyatīti padacatuṣṭayaṃ yojyam |",
    "1152:119": "prakārāntareṇāpi dūrīkaraṇādikamāha |",
    "1152:120": "astyeṣa ityādinā |",
    "1152:121": "bhavatyeṣa rūpādyabhisaṃbodhaparyāya ityarthaḥ |",
    "1152:122": "nanu &quot;dharmatayā rūpādyeva prajñāpāramite&quot;",
    "1152:123": "ti nyāyāt kathaṃ rūpādyavagamena māturdurīkaraṇādikamiti |",
    "1152:124": "tatkasya hetorityāśaṅkyāha |",
    "1152:125": "prajñāpāramitāyāṃ hītyādi |",
    "1152:126": "etaduktam |",
    "1152:127": "&quot;māyopamatayā yasmādrūpādyeva jinajananītyekasvabhāvatvena nyāyāt paridīpitāyāṃ prajñāpāramitāyāṃ pṛthagrūpādyavagamo viparyāsastasmādrūpādyavagamena māturdūrīkaṇādikami&quot;ti |",
    "1152:128": "mahārthatāmāha |",
    "1152:129": "mahāpāramiteyamityādinā |",
    "1152:130": "buddhamahārthasādhanānmahāpāramitā |",
    "1152:131": "tatra na mahatkaroti |",
    "1152:132": "adhikānutpādanāt |",
    "1152:133": "nālpīkaroti vyavasthitānapakarṣaṇāt |",
    "1152:134": "tadeva yathāyogaṃ kathayati |",
    "1152:135": "na saṃkṣipati na vikṣipatīti |",
    "1152:136": "&quot;prasiddhamātrasya hi yā&#39;",
    "1152:137": "yathārthatā",
    "1152:138": "tadarthasaṃbodhaphalaṃ hi śāsanam |&quot;",
    "1152:139": "iti bhāvaḥ | na balīkaroti |",
    "1152:140": "apūrvasamāropāt |",
    "1152:141": "na durbalīkaroti vidyamānānupavādāt |",
    "1152:142": "pṛthagjanavyavasthāyāṃ viparyāsabalādalpīyasī sarvajñatā muktyavasthāyāṃ mātuḥ sāmarthyena viparyāsāpagamānmahatī jātā |",
    "1152:143": "tatkathamevaṃ vakṣyata iti |",
    "1152:144": "tatkasya hetorityāśaṅkyāha |",
    "1152:145": "asaṃkṣiptā hītyādi |",
    "1152:146": "etaduktam |",
    "1152:147": "&quot;viparyāsāpagame mātuḥ sāmarthyasya sthitatvena yasmāt sarvajñatā&#39;",
    "1152:148": "saṃkṣiptā&#39;",
    "1152:149": "vikṣiptā tasmānna mahatī nālpīkriyata&quot;iti |",
    "1152:150": "tatrāpyabhiniveśo bandhanamityāha |",
    "1152:151": "sacedevamityādi |",
    "1152:152": "kimpunarevaṃ sañjānāna iti |",
    "1152:153": "vakṣyamāṇopalambhaṃ pratipadyamānaḥ kiṃ punaḥ prajñāpāramitāyāñcaratyapi tu mahopalambhatvānnaivetyarthaḥ |",
    "1152:154": "nanūpalambhasya ko doṣo yena tat sadbhāvānna caratīti |",
    "1152:155": "tatkasya hetorityāśaṅkyāha |",
    "1152:156": "na hyeṣa ityādi |",
    "1152:157": "etaduktam |",
    "1152:158": "&quot;yasmādeṣa prajñāpāramitāyāḥ sadṛśaḥ syando niṣyandastadanurūpaṃ phalaṃ sattvanirvāṇopalambho na bhavati |",
    "1152:159": "tasmādupalambhabhāvānna caratī&quot;ti |",
    "1152:160": "kathaṃ punaretaditi |",
    "1152:161": "tatkasya hetorityāśaṅkyāha |",
    "1152:162": "sattvāsvabhāvetyādi |",
    "1152:163": "sattvānāmasvabhāva eva jātiḥ prakṛtiryasyā iti sā tathoktā |",
    "1152:164": "evaṃ manyate sattvānutpādaprakṛtikāyā mātuḥ kathaṃ sattvopalambho niṣyandaphalamiti |",
    "1152:165": "sattvānutpādarūpatārthamevāha |",
    "1152:166": "sattvāsvabhāvatayetyādi |",
    "1152:167": "tatrāsvabhāvatāḥ viviktatā&#39;",
    "1152:168": "cintyatā yathākramaṃ kalpitāderveditavyā |",
    "1152:169": "sattvāvināśadharmatā sadaivāvasthitā tathatā |",
    "1152:170": "sattvasya māyopamatayā darśanamārgeṇānavagamaḥ sattvānabhisambodhanatā |",
    "1152:171": "sattvasya pūrvabhāvanāmārgeṇā&#39;",
    "1152:172": "pratipattiḥ sattvayathābhūtārthānabhisambodhanatā |",
    "1152:173": "sattvasya balaṃ pramāṇāvyāhataṃ sāmarthyaṃ māyopamatvaṃ tasya prāptiḥ samudāgamanatā |",
    "1152:174": "tayā tathāgatabalasya prajñāpāramitāyāḥ samudāgamanatā veditavyā |",
    "1152:175": "yathoktasvabhāvādilakṣaṇa evābhinirhārabhāvanāmārgo&#39;",
    "1152:176": "vasātavyaḥ |",
    "1152:177": "tathā coktam |",
    "1152:178": "svabhāvaḥ śreṣṭhatā tasya sarvasyānabhisaṃskṛtiḥ |",
    "1152:179": "nopalambhena dharmāṇāmarpaṇā ca mahārthatā ||21|| iti",
    "1152:180": "tadanantaraṃ dvitīyo&#39;",
    "1152:181": "tyantaviśuddhilakṣaṇo bhāvayitavyastadutpādānutpādahetoryathākramaṃ parigrahatyāgenetyutpādahetuṃ tāvatpratipādayitumāha |",
    "1152:182": "yo bhagavannityādi |",
    "1152:183": "mārgāntarākāṃkṣaṇānna kāṃkṣiṣyati |",
    "1152:184": "sandehābhāvānna vicikitsiṣyati |",
    "1152:185": "ajñānavigamānna dhanvāyiṣyati |",
    "1152:186": "ciracaritāvīti |",
    "1152:187": "ciraṃ dīrghakālaṃ caritamanuṣṭhitaṃ dānādi |",
    "1152:188": "śrāvakādibodhāvaniryātanenāvituṃ rakṣituṃ śīlamasyeti tathoktaḥ |",
    "1152:189": "anugamiṣyati dharmato&#39;rthataśca |",
    "1152:190": "anubhotsyate tannayataḥ |",
    "1152:191": "anubodhayiṣyati parānubhayathā yathākramamityevamarthabhedo vācyaḥ |",
    "1152:192": "parivārādidānātparyupāsyaḥ |",
    "1152:193": "saṃśayārthaparipṛcchanāt paripṛcchyeti buddhasevā kathitā |",
    "1152:194": "adhimokṣasya paryupāsanādinā kaḥ sambandho yenādhimokṣabalāt paryupāsanādikaṃ pratīyata iti |",
    "1152:195": "tatkasya hetorityāśaṅkyāha |",
    "1152:196": "yaḥ kaścidityādi |",
    "1152:197": "etaduktam |",
    "1152:198": "&quot;viśiṣṭakāraṇamantareṇa tādṛgvidhādhimokṣādyasambhavāt tatkāraṇaṃ tathāgataparyupāsanādikamanumīyata&quot;iti |",
    "1152:199": "samādhānotpādanācchrotramavadadhāti |",
    "1152:200": "maṇḍalādikaraṇātsatkṛtya śṛṇoti |",
    "1152:201": "aprastutārthānabhidhānāt kathaṃ nopacchinatti |",
    "1152:202": "ciracaritāvī sa iti vacanena dānādiruktaḥ |",
    "1152:203": "anekabuddhaparyupāsanāt bahubuddhaparyupāsitaḥ |",
    "1152:204": "sahetukaśravaṇādāvanabhiniveśaṃ pratipādayitumāha |",
    "1152:205": "śakyā punarityādi |",
    "1152:206": "upalakṣayitumityādipadāni yathāsaṃkhyamiyaṃ setyādi padacatuṣṭayena sambandhanīyāni |",
    "1152:207": "tatrākāraliṅganimittāni svasāmānyobhayarūpāṇi yathākramaṃ veditavyāni |",
    "1152:208": "hetubalādapi śravaṇaṃ saṃvṛtyā na tu tattvata ityāha |",
    "1152:209": "no hīdamiti |",
    "1152:210": "tadevāha |",
    "1152:211": "neyamityādi |",
    "1152:212": "pratīyamānenāpi skandhādinā kathaṃ na śakyate śravaṇādi kartumiti |",
    "1152:213": "tatkasya hetorityāśaṅkyāha |",
    "1152:214": "sarvadharmetyādi |",
    "1152:215": "tatra vartamānībhūtaskandhādisvalakṣaṇaśūnyatvāt sarvadharmaviviktatvaṃ kāryakāraṇāntadvayavigamādatyantaviviktatvam |",
    "1152:216": "tasmāt traiyadhvikaśūnyatvena tattvataḥ skandhādibhirnirdeṣṭuṃ na śakyata iti vākyārthaḥ |",
    "1152:217": "tadvyatirekeṇa tarhi nirdiśyatāmityāha |",
    "1152:218": "na cānyatretyādi |",
    "1152:219": "prakārāntarasyāniṣedhe kathamevaṃ labhyata iti |",
    "1152:220": "tatkasya hetorityāśaṅkyāha |",
    "1152:221": "skandhetyādi |",
    "1152:222": "utpādahetuvaikalyena śūnyam |",
    "1152:223": "svarūpānavadhāraṇādviviktam |",
    "1152:224": "kāryasāmarthyaviraheṇa śāntam |",
    "1152:225": "etaduktam |",
    "1152:226": "&quot;sarvadharmasaṃgrāhakaskandhādīnāṃ tattvato niḥsvabhāvatve tadvyatirekeṇa nirdeṣṭuṃ na śakyata&quot;ityādi |",
    "1152:227": "iti |",
    "1152:228": "hītyādyupasaṃhāraḥ |",
    "1152:229": "saṃjñā samajñā yathākramaṃ svasāmānyalakṣaṇodgrahaṇalakṣaṇe |",
    "1152:230": "prajñaptistatsaṅketodgrahaṇam |",
    "1152:231": "vyavahāraḥ prajñaptipūrvakau hitāhitaprāptiparihārau |",
    "1152:232": "vibhajyetyādi |",
    "1152:233": "prajñāpāramitāyogārthaṃ yenopāyakauśalaṃ vimātratayā mṛdvādibhedena bhāvitaṃ sa yogamāpatsyata iti vibhajya vaktavyametadanenopāyakauśalamuktam |",
    "1152:234": "yathoktameva sevāditrayamutpādahetuḥ |",
    "1152:235": "tathā coktam |",
    "1152:236": "buddhasevā ca dānādirupāye yacca kauśalam |",
    "1152:237": "hetavo&#39;trādhimokṣasya ||",
    "1152:238": "iti | anutpādahetuṃ nirdiśannāha |",
    "1152:239": "syāt khalu punarityādi |",
    "1152:240": "anadhimokṣe kiṃ kāraṇamiti |",
    "1152:241": "tatkasya hetorityāśaṅkyāha |",
    "1152:242": "pūrvamapītyādi |",
    "1152:243": "tataḥ parṣadbhyo&#39;",
    "1152:244": "pakrāntā iti pratikṣepacitteneti śeṣaḥ prayogādyavasthātraye yathākramaṃ sañcitenetyādi vaktavyam |",
    "1152:245": "kāyāsannidhānānna kāyasāmagrī |",
    "1152:246": "cittavikṣepānna cittasāmagrī |",
    "1152:247": "pratyakṣānumānāgamapramāṇairyathāsaṃkhyaṃ na jānanti na paśyanti na budhyante |",
    "1152:248": "ata eva na vedayante parāniti śeṣaḥ|",
    "1152:249": "svarūpanirākaraṇāt pratyākhyāsyanti sāmarthyāpahnavāt pratikṣepsyanti |",
    "1152:250": "apriyābhidhānāt pratikrokṣyanti |",
    "1152:251": "kuśalamūlānutpādādupahatyākuśalavāsanotpādena dagdhāḥ svalpadānāditrayayogādalpapuṇyāḥ |",
    "1152:252": "mṛdumaitryādisambhavādalpakuśalamūlāḥ |",
    "1152:253": "kartukāmatāpanayanādvicchandayiṣyanti |",
    "1152:254": "svarūpāpakarṣaṇakaraṇādvivecayiṣyanti |",
    "1152:255": "punaḥ pravṛttinirākaraṇādvivartayiṣyanti |",
    "1152:256": "sarveṇetyādi |",
    "1152:257": "sarveṇa buddharatnādirūpeṇa |",
    "1152:258": "sarvaṃ śākyamunitathāgatādirūpam |",
    "1152:259": "sarvathā mṛdumṛdvādiprakārabhedena sarvamadhiśīlādiprakāram |",
    "1152:260": "utpādanādupasthitena |",
    "1152:261": "vināśābhāvātsamutthāpitena |",
    "1152:262": "mahānirayeṣviti |",
    "1152:263": "jambūdvīpasyādho viṃśatyā yojanasahasrairavīcirmahānarakaḥ |",
    "1152:264": "tatpramāṇastadupariṣṭāt pratāpanastapano mahārauravo rauravaḥ saṃhātaḥ kālasūtraḥ sañjīvaścetyaṣṭau mahānirayāḥ |",
    "1152:265": "tejaḥsaṃvartanīti |",
    "1152:266": "narakagatimupādāya yāvadvrahmaloke kaścit sattvo nāviśiṣṭo bhavati tadā śūnyabhājane sapta sūryāḥ prādurbhūya krameṇāpmaṇḍalamārabhya yāvat prathamaṃ dhyānaṃ dahanti |",
    "1152:267": "anyeṣu lokadhātuṣviti |",
    "1152:268": "trisāhasramahāsāhasreṣu pracuraduḥkhānubhave kiṃ kāraṇamiti |",
    "1152:269": "tatkasya hetorityāśaṅkyāha |",
    "1152:270": "yathāpi nāmetyādi sugamaḥ |",
    "1152:271": "pañceti |",
    "1152:272": "mātṛvadhaḥ pitṛvadho&#39;",
    "1152:273": "rhadvadhaḥ saṅghabhedastathāgataduṣṭacittarudhirotpādaścetyetāni pañcakarmāṇyanantaramavīcimahāniraye janmahetutvādānantaryāṇi |",
    "1152:274": "kāryakāraṇasvabhāvaistribhiḥ sādṛśyābhāvādyathākramaṃ na prativarṇakāpi nānurūpāṇyapi na pratirūpāṇyapīti |",
    "1152:275": "yojyam |",
    "1152:276": "nanu duḥkhiteṣu karuṇāpravartanāt kathaṃ sthānādiniṣedha iti |",
    "1152:277": "tatkasya hetorityāśaṅkyāha |",
    "1152:278": "dharmadūṣakā hītyādi |",
    "1152:279": "anyeṣāmapi svadoṣopādānāt kasambakajātāḥ |",
    "1152:280": "sasyopaghāṭakatṛṇajātivadbodhisattvasya vināśāt kṛṣṇānirjātikāḥ kṛṣṇasarpavaddveṣavāhulyāt kṛṣṇāhijātikāḥ |",
    "1152:281": "anayena vyasanamiti |",
    "1152:282": "yasmādevaṃvidhapāpakāribhiḥ saha kṛpā&#39;",
    "1152:283": "viṣayatvenāvasthāviṣayavibhāgādikaṃ parihṛtyādikarmikāḥ saṃvāsādinā&#39;",
    "1152:284": "neneti durācāreṇa vyasanamupaghāṭamāpatsyante tasmāddharmadūṣakā varjanīyā iti yāvat |",
    "1152:285": "dharmadūṣakāḥ ka ucyanta ityāha |",
    "1152:286": "ye cetyādi |",
    "1152:287": "sambhavatpramāṇasyākathane kiṃ kāraṇamiti |",
    "1152:288": "tatkasya hetorityāśaṅkyāha |",
    "1152:289": "mā tathārūpasyetyādi |",
    "1152:290": "yasmānmahannārakakāyapramāṇaṃ śrutvā duḥkhamahattvaṃ pratipadya mahābhayena sahasā pratipakṣasamudācārādivirodhenoṣṇarudhirāgamanādayaḥ syustasmānnākhyāyata iti samudāyārthaḥ |",
    "1152:291": "maraṇamātrakaṃ vā duḥkhamāgāḍhamābādhaṃ spṛśediti mṛdumadhyādhimātrabhedāduktam |",
    "1152:292": "paścimāyā janatāyā āloka iti aśuklakarmakāriṇaḥ |",
    "1152:293": "saṃvegotpādāddharmālokaḥ saṃvega iti taddhetutvāttathoktaḥ |",
    "1152:294": "susaṃvṛtakāyakarmavākkarmamanaskarmaṇeti yathākramaṃ smṛtisamprajanyatāmupādāya kāyikavācikamānasikakuśalānuṣṭhānāduktam |",
    "1152:295": "viparītakaraṇe ko doṣa iti |",
    "1152:296": "tatkasya hetorityāśaṅkyāha |",
    "1152:297": "yatra hi nāmetyādi |",
    "1152:298": "evaṃrūpeṇeti naitadbuddhavacanamityevaṃ svabhāvenāsyopalakṣaṇaparatvāt |",
    "1152:299": "viparītakāyavāṅmanaskarmaṇāpīti jñeyam |",
    "1152:300": "prakrāntavāgdurbhāṣitaprakaraṇopasaṃhārārthamāha |",
    "1152:301": "katamenetyādi |",
    "1152:302": "anyathānantaramevoktamiti kathaṃ praśnaḥ syāt |",
    "1152:303": "mohapuruṣā iti |",
    "1152:304": "svake&#39;vatārāt svasyaiva vinayadarśanādapi |",
    "1152:305": "audāryādapi |",
    "1152:306": "gāmbhīryādaviruddhaiva dharmateti vacanāt |",
    "1152:307": "yatsūtre&#39;vatarati vinaye ca sandṛśyate |",
    "1152:308": "dharmatāñcānulomayatīti buddhabhāṣitalakṣaṇāvagamena sūtrādisaṅgṛhītāyā mātuḥ svabhāvānavadhāraṇānmūḍhaḥ |",
    "1152:309": "syādetannikāyagranthe parimitaparimāṇasūtreṣvanavatārāttathāparicchinnapramāṇavinayapiṭake&#39;",
    "1152:310": "saṃdarśanāttathāvyavasthāpitapudgalanairātmyādidharmatāvilomanenābuddhavacanamahāyānapratikṣepādamoha iti |",
    "1152:311": "evaṃ ca sati,",
    "1152:312": "muktakasūtrāṇyapi sūtrāntapiṭakeṣvapaṭhitatvādabuddhavacanānyabhyupeyāni syustathaikaikasmin sūtrāntapiṭake&#39;",
    "1152:313": "nyāni sūtrāntapiṭakāni na sarvaprakāramavataranti |",
    "1152:314": "tathaikaikasmin vinaye&#39;",
    "1152:315": "nye vinayā na sarvaprakāraṃ sandṛśyante |",
    "1152:316": "tathaikaikasmin nikāye yā dharmatā vyavasthāpitā na sā&#39;",
    "1152:317": "nyeṣu nikāyeṣu dharmatāṃ sarvaprakāramanulomayatītyevamaṣṭādaśabhedabhinnāni sūtravinayābhidharmapiṭakāni parasparaṃ granthārthavyatibhinnāni kathaṃ buddhavacanāni siddhyantītyavyāpakametat buddhavacanalakṣaṇamabhyupagacchantīti mūḍhā eva | athavā |",
    "1152:318": "manaḥpradoṣaḥ prakṛtipraduṣṭe",
    "1152:319": "hyayuktarūpe&#39;",
    "1152:320": "pi na yuktarūpaḥ |",
    "1152:321": "prāgeva sandehagatasya dharme",
    "1152:322": "tasmādupekṣaiva varaṃ hyadoṣaḥ ||",
    "1152:323": "ityasyārthasyāparijñānānmohapuruṣāḥ |",
    "1152:324": "dūṣayitavyāmiti |",
    "1152:325": "parasparavirodhodbhāvanayā pratikṣeptavyāmiti pūrvavat |",
    "1152:326": "pratibādhitavyāmiti pratyakṣādipramāṇabādhanāt |",
    "1152:327": "asya tu sarvadharmapratikṣepasya caturo hetūn pratipādayitumāha |",
    "1152:328": "ko&#39;tra heturityādi |",
    "1152:329": "caturbhirākārairiti |",
    "1152:330": "mārādhiṣṭhānagambhīradharmānadhimokṣaskandhādyabhiniveśapāpamitraparigrahaiścaturbhiḥ pratikṣepahetubhirityarthaḥ |",
    "1152:331": "tathā coktam |",
    "1152:332": "dharmavyasanahetavaḥ ||26||",
    "1152:333": "mārādhiṣṭhānagambhīradharmatānadhimuktate |",
    "1152:334": "skandhādyabhiniveśaśca pāpamitraparigrahaḥ ||27||iti",
    "1152:335": "abhisamayālaṅkārālokāyāṃ prajñāpāramitāvyākhyāyāṃ nirayaparivarto nāma saptamaḥ ||"
}